path.id: Both the teams finally decided to partner with each other and help each other throughout the iGEM Journey to finally accomplish our projects.

We started meeting regularly every week to discuss updates about our project and how we could help each other. A common discord channel for the two teams was initated for continuours interaction between two teams.
We met with UCSC iGEM Team on 19th July for the first time on google meet and presented each others projects and had a chat together. We found a similarity in our projects goals.
